4 SYNOPSIS:
5 This bill makes supplemental appropriations for
6 the fiscal year ending September 30, 2026, from the
7 Opioid Treatment and Abatement Fund to the entities
8 and for the purposes specified herein in the amount of
9 $43,138,650.
10 This bill would also transfer $5,000,000 that
11 was appropriated from the Opioid Treatment and
12 Abatement Fund to the Department of Mental Health in
13 Act 2025-255 of the 2025 Regular Session for a
14 dedicated opioid treatment center to the Department of
15 Public Health and would appropriate those funds to the
16 Department of Public Health for the same purpose.
